## Aurora Recon Framework

Automated recon tool for CTF/pentest labs. Authorized use only.

## Usage
python3 aurora.py -t <IP> [--fast|--full] [--htb] [--silent]

## Flags
-t / --target     Target IP
--fast            Top 100 ports
--full            All 65535 ports  
--htb             HTB mode (SecLists wordlist, shorter timeout)
--quick           Nmap only, skip modules
--silent          No output (for scripting)
--notes "text"    Add notes to report (repeatable)
-o                Output directory

## Output
aurora_<IP>_<timestamp>/
├── nmap.txt
├── http_<port>.txt
├── smb.txt / ssh_<port>.txt
└── report.json